ates\n| Asa H. Coon, 14\n| 1 dead\n| 4 injured\n| [[SuccessTech Academy shooting]]. 14-year-old student Asa Coon, reportedly upset about a school suspension, went on a shooting spree at [[SuccessTech Academy]], an [[alternative high school]] in [[Cleveland]], [[Ohio]], wounding two students and two teachers. He then fatally shot himself in a classroom.<ref name=\"NYTimes 2007-10-11\">{{cite news|first=Chris|last=Maag|author2=Ian Urbina  |title=Student, 14, Shoots 4 and Kills Himself in Cleveland School|date=2007-10-10|url =https://www.nytimes.com/2007/10/11/us/11cleveland.html?_r=1&hp&oref=slogin|work=[[The New York Times]]|accessdate = 2009-02-25}}</ref><ref name=\"clevelandfourshot\">{{cite news|title = Four shot at school, gunman kills himself|newspaper= [[The Plain Dealer]]|date = October 11, 2007|url = http://www.cleveland.com/schoolshooting/plaindealer/index.ssf?/schoolshooting/more/four_shot.html|first = Michael|last = O' Malley|author2 = Gabriel Baird|accessdate = 2009-03-01|url-status = dead|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090413185847/http://www.cleveland.com/schoolshooting/plaindealer/index.ssf?%2Fschoolshooting%2Fmore%2Ffour_shot.html|archivedate = April 13, 2009}}</ref><ref name=\"washington1011\">{{cite news|first=Joe|last=Milicia|title=4 Hurt, Gunman Killed in Ohio School|date=2007-10-11|url =https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/10/10/AR2007101001486.html|work=[[The Washington Post]]|accessdate = 2009-03-07}}</ref>\n|-\n| October 11, 2007\n| [[Amsterdam]], Netherlands\n| H\u00fcseyin P., 14\n| 1 dead\n|\n| A 14-year-old student, identified only as H\u00fcseyin P., stabbed 16-year-old classmate Youssef Mokhtari to death at a school in the [[Slotervaart (former borough)|Slotervaart]] borough of [[Amsterdam]]. The victim had reportedly made a joke about the surname of the perpetrator.<ref name=\"adnl12loct\">{{cite news|first=Tonny|last=van der Mee|author2=Robin Rotman  |title=Dader steekpartij dreigde eerder|date=2007-10-12|work=[[Algemeen Dagblad]]|url =http://www.ad.nl/amsterdam/stad/article1737946.ece|accessdate = 2009-04-18|language = Dutch}}</ref>\n|-\n| November 7, 2007\n| [[Tuusula]], Finland\n| Pekka-Eric Auvinen, 18\n| 9 dead\n| 1 injured\n| [[Jokela school shooting]]. 18-year-old student Pekka-Eric Auvinen opened fire with a [[.22 Long Rifle|.22-caliber]] [[semi-automatic handgun|semi-automatic]] [[SIG Mosquito|SIG Mosquito pistol]] at [[Jokela High School]], in [[Tuusula]], Finland. Six students, the school principal, and the school nurse were killed. The forty-minute attack ended when Auvinen shot himself in the head, later dying that evening at a [[Helsinki]] hospital.\n|-\n| December 11, 2007\n| [[Gurgaon]],<br>[[Haryana]],<br>India\n| Akash Vadav, 14;<br>Vikas Yadav, 13\n| 1 dead\n|\n| 14-year-old student Abhishek Tyagi was shot five times at the Euro International School, in [[Gurgaon]], India. Two other students, 14-year-old Akash Vadav and 13-year-old Vikas Yadav, were charged in connection with the shooting.<ref name=\"hindustani1212\">{{cite news|title=School students shoot classmate for \u2018bullying\u2019|date=2007-12-12|url =http://hindustantimes.com/StoryPage/StoryPage.aspx?id=df416321-98a6-4572-b0bf-c6c5fbf29902&MatchID1=4604&TeamID1=6&TeamID2=7&MatchType1=1&SeriesID1=1157&MatchID2=4575&TeamID3=8&TeamID4=2&MatchType2=1&SeriesID2=1147&PrimaryID=4604&Headline=School+students+shoot+classmate+for+%e2%80%98bullying%e2%80%99|work=[[Hindustan Times]]|accessdate = 2009-04-25}}</ref>\n|-\n| December 21, 2007\n| [[Union City, California|Union City]],<br>[[California]],<br>United States\n| Unknown\n| 1 dead\n|\n| Vernon Matthew Eddins, a 14-year-old student of [[James Logan High School]], was shot dead at the doorstep of Barnard-White Middle School, in [[Union City, California]].<ref name=\"usatodayviolencemap\">{{cite news|title=Mapping school violence|date=2009-04-12|agency= [[Associated Press]]|url =https://www.usatoday.com/news/nation/graphic-school-killings.htm|