d)|Breakfast Club]]\n| for the TV series [[Pinoy Big Brother]] with the contestants [[Riza Santos]], [[Megan Young]], [[Gaby dela Merced]], [[Victor Basa]] and [[Mcoy Fundales]]\n| [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VDwXKrQjn9I]\n|-\n| {{dts|2007-11-15}}\n| \"[[Hare Hare Yukai]]\"\n| [[Aya Hirano]], [[Minori Chihara]] and [[Yuko Goto]] from ''[[The Melancholy of Haruhi Suzumiya]]''\n| --\n| [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5Xx4tszZ-DE]\n|-\n| {{dts|2007-12-21}}\n| \"[[Jump (for My Love)]]\"\n| [[The Pointer Sisters]]\n| --\n| [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RXbfCQ6eV_I]\n|-\n| {{dts|2008-01-18|addkey=1}}\n| CPDRC Sinulog 2008\n| --\n| homage to [[Santo Ni\u00f1o de Ceb\u00fa|Santo Ni\u00f1o]] because of the [[Sinulog|Sinulog festival]]; featuring the song \"Marching Band Medley\" from the movie [[Drumline (film)|Drumline]]\n| [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-zHwMBNMtV4]\n|-\n| {{dts|2008-01-18|addkey=2}}\n| \"Mabuhi ka GWEN\"\n| --\n| with [[Gwendolyn Garcia]], then Governor of [[Cebu]]; featuring the Cebuano song \"Mabuhi ka Sogbuanon\"\n| [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7Waaq8cb39Q]\n|-\n| {{dts|2008-02-23}}\n| \"[[Crank That (Soulja Boy)]]\" / \"[[U Can't Touch This]]\"\n| [[Soulja Boy]] / [[MC Hammer]]\n| Audio was muted after 7 million views because of copyright<br />Video reuploaded to [[Metacafe]]\n| [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yYp2Aloz-uE] [http://www.metacafe.com/watch/5619080/souljaboy/]\n|-\n| {{dts|2008-04-02}}\n| \"[[Gloria (Umberto Tozzi song)|Gloria]]\"\n| [[Laura Branigan]]\n| Audio was changed on the original video due to [[copyright]] issues. Video reuploaded to Metacafe\n| [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MasbNiEiKkI] [http://www.metacafe.com/watch/5621992/gloria/]\n|-\n| {{dts|2008-04-28}}\n| \"[[Holding Out for a Hero]]\"\n| [[Bonnie Tyler]]\n| --\n| [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fDdPuCsOLaQ]\n|-\n| {{dts|2008-06-28}}\n| \"[[Low (Flo Rida song)|Low]]\"\n| [[Flo Rida]] ft. [[T-Pain]]\n| --\n| [http://www.metacafe.com/watch/1452911/low/]\